===Etymology===
Named by its discoverer {{w|Paul Emile Lecoq de Boisbaudran|Lecoq}}, after {{der|en|la|Gallia|t=Gaul}}. It was claimed that Lecoq had named the element after himself, since {{m|la|gallus}} is the Latin translation of the {{noncog|fr|le [[coq]]}}, but Lecoq denied this in an article of 1877.

